      "body": "> Is it possible to allow the original node that broadcast the TX to send and hash the time along with the transaction.\n\nAnd nothing prevents you from just backdating your TX. You'd need something like [OpenTimestamps](https://github.com/opentimestamps)... But OpenTimestamps depends on the block chain, so you can just use it directly \"as is\", instead of walking in circles.\n",
